msgstr "Pytajće prašenja za pomoc, na kotrež móžeće wotmołwić"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:73
msgid "Start answering!"
msgstr "Pisajće swoju prěnju wotmołwu!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:78
msgid "Learn more about forum contribution"
msgstr "Dalše informacije wo sobuskutkowanju w forumje"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:85
msgid "1 → 1000"
msgstr "1 → 1000"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:86
msgid "Solving one issue helps up to 1000 users a day"
msgstr "Rozrisowanje jednoho problema pomha hač do 1.000 wužiwarjow na dźeń"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:92 svelte/contribute/Picker.svelte:25
msgid "Answer questions in the support forum"
msgstr "Wotmołwće na prašenja w forumje pomocy"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:93
msgid "Where all the action happens"
msgstr "Hdźež so wšitko stawa"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:95
msgid ""
"From hardcore web developers to \"how do I install Firefox\"\n"
"                    first time users, everybody needs your help in the forum!\n"
"                    Share your knowledge by pointing people to the right help\n"
"                    articles and providing troubleshooting steps for their\n"
"                    individual questions."
msgstr ""
"Wot pokročenych webwuwiwarjow\n"
"                     do započatkarjow, kotřiž so prašeja, kak dyrbja „Firefox instalować“, kóždy trjeba swoju pomoc w forumje!\n"
"                     Dźělće swoje znajomosće a pokazajće ludźom prawe\n"
"                     nastawki pomocy a poskićće kroki za rozrisanje problemow za jich\n"
"                     indiwiduelne prašenja."

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:105
msgid "Help articles"
msgstr "Nastawki pomocy"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:124
msgid "Explore the Knowledge Base Dashboard"
msgstr "Wuslědźće wědowu datowu banku"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:133
msgid "Check the Needs Update column and start editing articles!"
msgstr "Přepruwujće špaltu „Trjeba aktualizaciju“ a započńće nastawki wobdźěłować!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:142
msgid "Learn more about KB contribution"
msgstr "Dalše informacije wo sobuskutkowanju we wědowej datowej bance"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:147 svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:203
msgid "400 → 70+"
msgstr "400 → 70+"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:148 svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:204
msgid "One article can be viewed by 400 million users and translated into 70+ languages"
msgstr "Jedyn nastawk da so wot 400 milionow wužiwarjow wobhladować a do přez 70 rěčow přełožować"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:154
msgid "Help us write help articles"
msgstr "Pomhajće nam nastawki pomocy pisać"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:155
msgid "Share your wisdom with the world!"
msgstr "Dźělće swoju mudrosć ze swětom!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:157
msgid ""
"If you like writing and teaching, then the Knowledge Base (KB) is the place for you. We need contributors that can write, edit or proofread articles in English. Thousands of people are accessing our"
" Knowledge Base every week. Imagine how many will be helped by you!"
msgstr ""
"Jeli rady pisaće a wučiće, da je wědowa datowa banka (KB) prawe městno za was. Trjebamy sobuskutkowarjow, kotřiž móža nastawki pisać, wobdźěłować abo korigować. Tysacy ludźi maja kóždy tydźeń "
"přistup k našej wědowej datowej bance. Předstajće sej, kak wjele ludźi wot was pomoć dóstawa!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:165
msgid "Localization"
msgstr "Lokalizacija"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:180
msgid "Check if your locale is available and go to your localization dashboard"
msgstr "Kontrolujće, hač waša rěč je k dispoziciji a dźiće k swojej lokalizaciskej desce"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:189
msgid "Start localizing an article!"
msgstr "Započńće nastawk lokalizować!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:196
msgid "Learn more about localization contribution"
msgstr "Dalše informacije wo sobuskutkowanju při lokalizowanju"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:210
msgid "Help us localize support articles"
msgstr "Pomhajće nam nastawki pomocy lokalizować"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:212
msgid "Let’s make Mozilla Support speak your language!"
msgstr "Dajmy pomocy Mozilla wašu rěč rěčeć!"

#: svelte/contribute/Contribute.svelte:215
msgid "Help articles are not available in your language yet? You want to join the amazing team translating them? You will help millions of users in your language. Pretty heroic, right?"
msgstr "Su nastawki, kotrež hišće we wašej rěči njejsu? Chceće so wulkotnemu teamej přidružić, kotryž je přełožuje? Z tym pomhaće milionam wužiwarjow w swojej rěči. Chětro heroiske, něwěrno?"

#: svelte/contribute/Header.svelte:13
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Startowa strona"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:18
msgid "Save the world from the comfort of your couch"
msgstr "Wuchowajće swět ze swojeho mjechkeho konopeja"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:21
msgid "Help millions of users get the most out of their favorite browser. Your contributions will reach millions of users worldwide, and you can do it from the comfort of your couch!"
msgstr "Pomhajće milionam wužiwarjow najlěpše z jich wobhladowaka won ćahnyć. Waše přinoški dosćahnu milionow wužiwarjow swětodaloko, a wy móžeće to ze swojeho mjechkeho konopeja činić!"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:26
msgid "We need your help!"
msgstr "Trjebamy wašu pomoc!"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:29
msgid "Used by more than 400 million people, Mozilla support is fully powered by volunteers, and it’s more important than ever. This is where you come in."
msgstr "Pomoc Mozilla, kotruž wjace hač 400 milionow ludźi wužiwa, zepěra so jenož na dobrowólnikow a je wažniša hač do toho. Tu dóńdźeće wy do hry."

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:39
msgid "About us"
msgstr "Wo nas"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:41
msgid "Mozilla Support is a community of enthusiastic volunteers and employees trying to support our users around the globe. Join us for an incredible adventure!"
msgstr "Pomoc Mozilla je zhromadźenstwo zahorjenych dobrowólnikow a přistajenych, kotřiž pospytuja, našich wužiwarjow na cyłym swěće podpěrować. Čińće sobu a dožiwće njewěrjomny dyrdomdej!"

#: svelte/contribute/Landing.svelte:54
msgid "Photo of Mozilla staff and volunteers."
msgstr "Foto sobudźěłaćerjow a dobrowólnikow Mozilla."

